OL,3,CMinister to get power to veto
OL,4,Csentencing guidance after 'two-tier'
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FA Cabinet minister will be given the
OL,8,Fpower to veto any changes to
OL,9,Fsentencing guidelines proposed by an
OL,10,Findependent body, following a row over
OL,11,Fclaims of "two-tier" justice.
OL,13,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood said
OL,14,Fshe wanted to "right the democratic
OL,15,Fdeficit that has been uncovered" by
OL,16,Fintroducing a requirement for any new
OL,17,Frules to be approved by her.
