OL,3,CMinister to get power to veto
OL,4,Csentencing guidance after 'two-tier'
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FIt comes after ministers intervened to
OL,8,Fblock updated Sentencing Council
OL,9,Fguidance which would have meant judges
OL,10,Fshould consider the background of
OL,11,Foffenders from certain minority groups
OL,12,Fwhen deciding on a punishment.
OL,14,FUnder new rules announced on Tuesday,
OL,15,Fthe independent Council, which is made
OL,16,Fup of some of the most senior legal
OL,17,Ffigures in England and Wales, will be
OL,18,Funable to issue any changes without
OL,19,Fministerial oversight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
