OL,3,CMinister to get power to veto
OL,4,Csentencing guidance after 'two-tier'
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FBoth the Justice Secretary and the
OL,8,FLady Chief Justice, who is the head of
OL,9,Fthe judiciary, will need to give the
OL,10,Fgreen light in order for any new
OL,11,Fdirective to be finalised.
OL,13,FThe Government insisted the new powers
OL,14,Fdo not interfere with the independence
OL,15,Fof judges but seek to ensure a
OL,16,F"democratic lock" and block the
OL,17,FCouncil from "setting policy" without
OL,18,Fthe involvement of Parliament.
