OL,4,Csentencing guidance after 'two-tier'
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FThe changes will be brought in as part
OL,8,Fof the Sentencing Bill, introduced in
OL,9,Fthe House of Commons on Tuesday.
OL,11,FAlso written into the legislation are
OL,12,Fmeasures aimed at tackling prison
OL,13,Fovercrowding, including what the
OL,14,FMinistry of Justice describes as
OL,15,F"Texas-style earned release sentences".
OL,17,FThe Justice Secretary said:
OL,18,F"Individual sentencing decisions will
OL,19,Falways be the responsibility of the
OL,20,Findependent judiciary ` and this is
OL,21,Fsomething I will staunchly defend.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@fO]zD@AOU
