OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FEarlier this year, Ms Mahmood had
OL,8,Fasked the Council to reconsider its
OL,9,Fguidance for judges but it rejected
OL,10,Fher request, arguing the rules would
OL,11,Fensure the courts had the "most
OL,12,Fcomprehensive information available"
OL,13,Fto hand out a punishment.
OL,15,FUnder the proposed rules, a pre-
OL,16,Fsentence report would have usually
OL,17,Fbeen necessary for offenders from an
OL,18,Fethnic, cultural or faith minority,
OL,19,Falongside other groups such as young
OL,20,Fadults aged 18 to 25 and pregnant
OL,21,Fwomen.
