OL,7,FBoth the Opposition and the Government
OL,8,Fcriticised the change, suggesting it
OL,9,Fleft open the prospect of what they
OL,10,Ftermed "two-tier" justice.
OL,12,FThe guidelines were abandoned after
OL,13,Fministers tabled an emergency law to
OL,14,Foverride them.
